{
  "id": "RAW_75841cfd",
  "title": "Ironwood：第七代 TPU 的关键特性解析",
  "url": "https://blog.google/products/google-cloud/ironwood-google-tpu-things-to-know/",
  "date": "2025-11-25 21:24:23",
  "author": "Ari Marini",
  "siteName": "The Keyword (blog.google) ",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <uni-article-speakable style=\"height: 55px; margin-bottom: 36px; display: block;\" page-title=\"3 things to know about Ironwood, our latest TPU\" listen-to-article=\"Listen to article\" data-date-modified=\"2025-11-25T21:24:23.335378+00:00\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-script-src=\"https://www.gstatic.com/readaloud/player/web/api/js/api.js\" data-highlight-mode=\"word-over-paragraph\">\n   <!---->\n   <div id=\"uni-article-speakable\">\n    <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n    <span width=\"14px\"> \n     <svg width=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 66 66\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"uni-spinner uni-spinner--small\">\n      <circle class=\"loader-path\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"7\" cx=\"33\" cy=\"33\" r=\"25\"></circle>\n     </svg> \n    </span>\n   </div>\n  </uni-article-speakable>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;3 things to know about Ironwood, our latest TPU&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"jkksh\" class=\"drop-cap\">Today's most advanced AI models, like those powering complex thinking and calculations, need speed and efficiency from the hardware that powers them. That's why at Cloud Next in April, we unveiled <a href=\"https://blog.google/products/google-cloud/ironwood-tpu-age-of-inference/\">Ironwood</a>, our seventh-generation Tensor Processing Unit (TPU).</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"A close-up of four Ironwood chips.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"3 things to know about Ironwood, our latest TPU\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;3 things to know about Ironwood, our latest TPU&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n    <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <img alt=\"A close-up of four Ironwood chips.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Ironwood_board.width-100.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Ironwood_board.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Ironwood_board.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\">\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n    <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n    <figcaption class=\"image-full-width__caption\">\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <div slot=\"caption-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <div class=\"rich-text\">\n       <p data-block-key=\"baej2\">Ironwood is our most powerful, capable, and energy-efficient TPU yet, designed to power thinking, inferential AI models at scale.</p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n    </figcaption>\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;3 things to know about Ironwood, our latest TPU&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"jkksh\">By acting as a hugely efficient parallel processor, Ironwood excels at managing massive calculations and significantly minimizes the internal time required for data to shuttle across the chip. This breakthrough dramatically speeds up complex AI, making models run significantly faster and smoother across our cloud.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"3fk30\">And now, Ironwood is here for Cloud customers.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"ds20c\">Here are three things to know about it.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"1rlor\">1. It’s purpose-built for the age of inference</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"d3k1c\">As the industry’s focus shifts from training frontier models to powering useful, responsive interactions with them, Ironwood provides the essential hardware. It’s custom built for high-volume, low-latency <a href=\"https://blog.google/technology/ai/ask-a-techspert-what-is-inference/\">AI inference</a> and model serving. It offers more than 4X better performance per chip for both training and inference workloads compared to <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/compute/trillium-tpu-is-ga?utm_source=keywordsnippet&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;e=48754805\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">our last generation</a>, making Ironwood our most powerful and energy-efficient custom silicon to date.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-related-content-tout title=\"Ask a Techspert: What's the difference …\" cta=\"See more\" summary=\"Learn more from a Google expert about CPUs, GPUs and TPUs — and Google latest TPU, Trillium.\" hideimage=\"False\" eyebrow=\"Related Article\" image-alt-text=\"Three squares illustrate different computer processors. Blue: a classic CPU with a grid of contact points. Green: a GPU with a simple line symbolizing parallel processing. Yellow: a TPU with intricate circuitry for machine learning.\" role=\"none\" fullurl=\"https://blog.google/technology/ai/difference-cpu-gpu-tpu-trillium/\" pagetype=\"articlepage\" isarticlepage=\"\" data-ga4-related-article=\"{\n  &quot;event&quot;: &quot;article_lead_click&quot;,\n  &quot;link_text&quot;: &quot;Ask a Techspert: What\\u0027s the difference between a CPU, GPU and TPU?&quot;,\n  &quot;link_type&quot;: &quot;internal&quot;,\n  &quot;full_url&quot;: &quot;https://blog.google/technology/ai/difference-cpu-gpu-tpu-trillium/&quot;,\n  &quot;title&quot;: &quot;Ask a Techspert: What\\u0027s the difference between a CPU, GPU and TPU?&quot;,\n  &quot;author&quot; : &quot;Molly McHugh-Johnson&quot;,\n  &quot;slug&quot;: &quot;difference-cpu-gpu-tpu-trillium&quot;,\n  &quot;position&quot;: &quot;1 of 1&quot;,\n  &quot;click_location&quot;: &quot;undefined&quot;,\n  &quot;primary_tag&quot;: &quot;Topics - AI&quot;,\n  &quot;secondary_tags&quot;: &quot;Google Cloud,Ask a Techspert&quot;,\n  &quot;published_date&quot;: &quot;2024-10-30|19:00&quot;,\n  &quot;hero_media_type&quot;: &quot;image&quot;,\n  &quot;days_since_published&quot;: &quot;391&quot;,\n  &quot;content_category&quot;: &quot;Editorial feature&quot;,\n  &quot;word_count&quot;: &quot;888&quot;,\n  &quot;has_audio&quot;: &quot;no&quot;,\n  &quot;has_video&quot;: &quot;no&quot;,\n  &quot;has_image&quot;: &quot;no&quot;,\n  &quot;has_carousel&quot;: &quot;no&quot;\n}\">\n   <!---->\n   <section role=\"none\" class=\" related-content-tout related-content-tout--max-width uni-component-spacing \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Related Content Tout&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Ask a Techspert: What's the difference …&quot;}\">\n    <a class=\"related-content-tout__wrapper\" href=\"https://blog.google/technology/ai/difference-cpu-gpu-tpu-trillium/\" aria-label=\"\n      Related Article.\n      Three squares illustrate different computer processors. Blue: a classic CPU with a grid of contact points. Green: a GPU with a simple line symbolizing parallel processing. Yellow: a TPU with intricate circuitry for machine learning. Ask a Techspert: What's the difference ….\n      Learn more from a Google expert about CPUs, GPUs and TPUs — and Google latest TPU, Trillium. See more\"><!--?lit$671294996$--></a>\n   </section>\n  </uni-related-content-tout>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;3 things to know about Ironwood, our latest TPU&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"jkksh\">2. It’s a giant network of power</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"bef06\">TPUs are a key component of <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/solutions/ai-hypercomputer?e=48754805\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">AI Hypercomputer</a>, our integrated supercomputing system designed to boost system-level performance and efficiency across compute, networking, storage and software. At its core, the system groups individual TPUs into interconnected units called pods. With Ironwood, we can scale up to 9,216 chips in a superpod. These chips are linked via a breakthrough Inter-Chip Interconnect (ICI) network operating at 9.6 Tb/s.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"A fisheye view of a data center wall with rows of server racks, complex cabling and overhead cable trays.\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"3 things to know about Ironwood, our latest TPU\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;3 things to know about Ironwood, our latest TPU&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n    <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <img alt=\"A fisheye view of a data center wall with rows of server racks, complex cabling and overhead cable trays.\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Ironwood_superpod.width-100.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Ironwood_superpod.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Ironwood_superpod.width-1000.format-webp.webp&quot;\n          }\">\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n    <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n    <figcaption class=\"image-full-width__caption\">\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n     <div slot=\"caption-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <div class=\"rich-text\">\n       <p data-block-key=\"baej2\">Part of an Ironwood superpod, directly connecting 9,216 Ironwood TPUs in a single domain.</p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$671294996$-->\n    </figcaption>\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;3 things to know about Ironwood, our latest TPU&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"jkksh\">This massive connectivity allows thousands of chips to rapidly communicate and access a staggering 1.77 Petabytes of shared High Bandwidth Memory (HBM), overcoming data bottlenecks for even the most demanding models. This efficiency significantly reduces the compute-hours and energy required for training and running cutting-edge AI services.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"7pmj9\">3. It’s designed for AI <i>with</i> AI</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"5fup7\">Ironwood is the result of a continuous loop at Google where researchers influence hardware design, and hardware accelerates research. While competitors rely on external vendors, when Google DeepMind needs a specific architectural advancement for a model like Gemini, they collaborate directly with their TPU engineer counterparts. As a result, our models are trained on the newest TPU generations, often seeing significant speedups over previous hardware. Our researchers even use AI to design the next chip generation — a method called <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/blog/how-alphachip-transformed-computer-chip-design/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">AlphaChip</a> — which has used reinforcement learning to generate superior layouts for the last three TPU generations, including Ironwood.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "谷歌 Ironwood 是专为高容量、低延迟 AI 推理打造的第七代 TPU，它显著提升了性能，通过超级集群实现了大规模扩展，并采用了 AI 技术优化设计。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "谷歌 Ironwood 是专为高容量、低延迟 AI 推理打造的第七代 TPU，它显著提升了性能，通过超级集群实现了大规模扩展，并采用了 AI 技术优化设计。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了谷歌的第七代张量处理单元 (TPU) Ironwood，重点介绍了其对高级 AI 推理模型的强大支持。Ironwood 专为高容量、低延迟的 AI 推理和模型服务而定制，与上一代产品相比，每个芯片的训练和推理工作负载性能提升超过 4 倍，使其成为谷歌迄今为止最强大、最节能的定制芯片。它是谷歌 AI 超算的核心组件，能够在超级集群中扩展到 9，216 个芯片，通过 9.6 Tb/s 的芯片间互连 (ICI) 网络互连，从而实现快速通信并访问 1.77 PB 的共享高带宽内存 (HBM)。值得一提的是，Ironwood 的设计过程本身就通过一种名为 AlphaChip 的方法利用 AI，其中强化学习生成卓越的芯片布局，从而在谷歌的 AI 研究人员和硬件工程师之间形成持续的创新循环。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Ironwood 专为 AI 推理应用时代而打造，提供卓越的性能和能源效率。",
      "explanation": "Ironwood 专为高容量、低延迟的 AI 推理和模型服务而设计，与前几代产品相比，每个芯片的训练和推理性能提升超过 4 倍，从而提高了现代 AI 应用程序的效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "TPU 架构为要求严苛的 AI 工作负载实现了大规模的可扩展性和高带宽通信。",
      "explanation": "Ironwood 在一个超级集群中可扩展到 9，216 个芯片，通过 9.6 Tb/s 的 ICI 网络连接，提供对 1.77 PB 共享 HBM 的访问，有效消除复杂模型的数据瓶颈。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Ironwood 的设计过程通过 AI 得到增强，从而在硬件和 AI 研究之间形成协同循环。",
